@startuml
!theme plain
skinparam dpi 180
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam packageStyle rectangle

title 图2 C4-Container 平台容器图

rectangle "Nursing-App System" {
  rectangle "Container A\nAdmin Web\nVue3 + Vite + Pinia" as C1
  rectangle "Container B\nMobile App\nFlutter + Riverpod" as C2
  rectangle "Container C\nBackend API\nSpring Boot + Security + MyBatis-Plus" as C3
  database "Container D\nMySQL" as C4
  queue "Container E\nRabbitMQ" as C5
}

cloud "External\nAliyun SMS" as E1
cloud "External\nAliyun Push" as E2
cloud "External\nAlipay" as E3
cloud "External\nAmap" as E4

C1 --> C3 : /api/v1/**
C2 --> C3 : /api/v1/**
C3 --> C4 : SQL + 事务
C3 --> C5 : 事件投递/消费
C3 --> E1 : 短信验证码
C3 --> E2 : 消息推送
C3 --> E3 : 支付与退款
C3 --> E4 : 地理服务

note right of C3
分层：
- Controller/API
- Service/领域规则
- Mapper/数据访问
- Task/定时任务
- Security/过滤链
end note

@enduml